Is a Free Online Martial Arts Magazine for the Martial Arts Community in the UK & Ireland. We provide local news from Martial Arts Clubs, Schools & Organisations in relation to Gradings, Competitions & Events. Feel Free to browse our website and feel free to submit an article with some text, a photo & a link you your facebook page or website so we can place a link to your website when we publish our next issue.
